dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours with 5 foot interval. Map shows provincial, district, planning area, municipal or township, property and cadastral boundaries. Includes index to sheets. "(N. A. 36, U. III. 11¹⁵)" "Surveyed (Oct. 1960) and drawn (May 1961) by Lands and Surveys Department, Uganda." "Crown copyright reserved." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of a right of way." "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "200-6-61."
